overview: Natasawak.com is an online shopping website offering discounted brand sales and local designers items. The Company delivers to worldwide destinations and especially the Middle East including Lebanon, UAE, Jordan, KSA, Qatar and Kuwait. Natasawak’s online shopping platform offers apparel, dresses, shoes, bags, accessories, kids wear, men’s wear, women’s fashion items, delicacies, vintage and artistic handmade products. Natasawak’s tagline is: “Elegant deals for elegant people”.
